> Have you looked at ScrollBehavior.buildScrollbar?

Indeed I have, but i can't find a way to apply it to mobile platforms as per the description `Applies a [RawScrollbar] to the child widget on desktop platforms` and as per the implementation 

```dart
Widget buildScrollbar(BuildContext context, Widget child, ScrollableDetails details) {
    // When modifying this function, consider modifying the implementation in
